videos.description: 1H (15:44) UCLA TJ Leaf made Dunk. Assisted by Bryce Alford.
videos.headline: UCLA's TJ Leaf gets open off a pick and roll for a two-handed slam dunk

videos.description: 1H (10:21) UCLA Gyorgy Goloman made Dunk. Assisted by Isaac Hamilton.
videos.headline: UCLA gets an alley-oop in transition

videos.description: From the logo at half-court, Isaac Hamilton throws the long distance alley-oop to Lonzo Ball for the huge dunk.
videos.headline: UCLA throws up alley-oop from nearly half-court
Lonzo Ball gets the ball off a Long Beach St turnover and finishes on the other end with a one-handed dunk

videos.description: 2H (10:53) UCLA Lonzo Ball made Dunk. Assisted by Bryce Alford.
videos.headline: L. Ball made Dunk. Assisted by B. Alford.

videos.description: Lonzo Ball is having himself a dunkfest against Long Beach State including Aaron Holiday throwing it off the backboard for Ball to throw down the two-handed alley-oop.
videos.headline: Off the backboard alley-oop? Thank you UCLA!
